quran[19]{c,v,t}:
  15,26,"Uye zvirokwazvo, takasika vanhu kubva kuivhu rakaoma rakasiyana-siyana"
  15,27,"Uye maJinn, takamasika kare kubva kumoto usina hutsi"
  15,28,"Uye (rangarira) apo Tenzi vako vakati kungirozi: “Zvirokwazvo, ndichasika munhu (Adam) kubva kuivhu rakaoma rakasiyana-siyana.”"
  15,29,"“Saka naizvozvo, kana ndichinge ndapedza kumushongedza uye ndafemera maari mweya wandakamusikira, ivai munomupfugamira moisa zviso zvenyu pasi.”"
  15,30,Naizvozvo ngirozi dzakava dzinopfugama nekuisa zviso zvadzo pasi pamwe chete
  15,31,Kusara kwa Iblees (Satani) akaramba kuva pakati peavo vanopfugama
  15,32,"Allah vakati: “Iwe Iblees (Satani)! Chikonzero chako ndecheyi kuti usave pakati peavo vakapfugama?”"
  15,33,"(Satani) akati: “Hazviite kuti ndipfugamire munhu, uyo wamakasika kubva kuivhu rakaoma rakasiyana-siyana.”"
  15,34,"(Allah) vakati: “Kana zvakadaro buda muno, zvirokwazvo, uri Rajeem (akashorwa).”"
  15,35,"“Uye zvirokwazvo, kutsamwa (kwaAllah) kuchange kuri pauri kusvika zuva rekutongwa.”"
  15,36,"(Satani) akati: “Tenzi vangu! Ndipeiwo nguva kusvikira zuva rekutongwa (zuva ravachamutswa kubva kuvafi).”"
  15,37,"(Allah) vakati: “Zvirokwazvo, uri pakati peavo vakapihwa nguva.”"
  15,38,“Kusvika zuva renguva yakatarwa.”
  15,39,"(Satani) akati: “Tenzi vangu! Nechikonzero chekuti mandirasisa gwara, zvirokwazvo, ndichavashongedzera (vanhu) nzira dzezvakaipa panyika, uye ndichavatsaudza vose mugwara rakatwasuka.”"
  15,40,“Kusara kwevaranda venyu vamakasarudza pakati pavo.”
  15,41,"(Allah) vakati: “Iyi ndiyo nzira yakatwasuka inotungamira kwandiri.”"
  15,42,"“Zvirokwazvo, hauna masimba kune varanda vangu, kusara kweavo vanokutevera vanoita zvakaipa uye vasingatendi.”"
  15,43,"“Uye zvirokwazvo, Gehena ndiyo nzvimbo irikuvimbiswa kwavari vose (pamwe chete).”"
  15,44,"“Rine (Gehena) misuwo minomwe, musuwo wese kubva kwavari une boka (revatadzi) rakatarwa.”"